<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天就是萬聖節喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對我而言，光是能迎來這特別的一天，<delay20 />
我就覺得很幸福了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家似乎都很認真地<delay20 />
做恐怖的裝扮呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是可怕啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Shaking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說回來，<delay20 />應該不會有真正的鬼怪<delay20 />
出現在萬聖節當天吧？</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不給糖<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就搗蛋<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不給糖<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就搗蛋<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為了當天<delay20 />能好好地說出來，<delay20 />
我得從現在開始練習才行，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />已經進入到萬聖節前的<delay20 />
倒數計時階段囉！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還沒準備好的話就得加快腳步了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />今天的<tag a="110" b="10" /><delay20 />
情緒很難得地相當亢奮呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都是因為這名為萬聖節的魔法的關係嗎？</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />萬聖節終於快開始了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也差不多該開始<delay20 />
先做準備<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？<delay20 />你問我做什麼準備？<10_4 />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那當然是為了提高裝扮的完成度，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />事先做好融入角色的意象訓練啊！</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這座島終於也開始<delay20 />
裝飾南瓜家具了喔。<delay20 />
我剛剛散步時有看到家具，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />看來有關注萬聖節的人，<delay20 />
不只我一個呢<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />隨著展示出來的南瓜家具變多，<delay20 />
萬聖節的氣氛<delay20 />也越來越濃厚了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要想到越接近活動當天，<delay20 />
這座島上的裝飾也會隨之增多……<delay20 />
我越來越期待活動到來啦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="8" />的景色<delay20 />
也被染上了萬聖節的顏色，<delay20 />
變得相當熱鬧呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />被如此大量萬聖節風格的<delay20 />
展示品所包圍，<delay20 />
感覺真是難以言喻啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />直到萬聖節的魔法解除前，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就讓我好好享受這景色吧<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
</msbt>